Message: The user completes the submission of the form
Hi, it is my first time running an add. I created an ad, and added a payment method. But it's not clear if the ad is running or not.

Hey there! Let's make sure your ad is running smoothly. First, check if you've received a notification about your ad being live. If not, it might still be in the approval process, which usually takes 1-2 business days. Also, ensure that you hit 'Save and Next' instead of just 'Save' when creating your campaign and ad set. If you need more detailed guidance, here's an article on creating your first ad: [How to create your first ad](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17618196971149-How-to-create-your-first-ad). Let me know if you have any other questions!
Ah. But if I scheduled the ad to run starting on saturday at 12AM.... and it's not approved by then. what will happen?

If your ad isn't approved by the scheduled start time, it will begin running as soon as it's approved. The system will automatically adjust to start the ad once it gets the green light. If you have any concerns or need further assistance, feel free to reach out!
You're welcome! If you have any more questions or need help, just let me know. Have a great day!
